WEBVTT

00:00:07.503 --> 00:00:11.424
Bad news: your worst enemies 
are at the gate.

00:00:11.424 --> 00:00:17.764
For your fledgling kingdom guards the 
world’s only herd of tiny dino creatures.

00:00:17.972 --> 00:00:19.599
To you, they’re sacred.

00:00:19.599 --> 00:00:21.809
To everyone else, they’re food.

00:00:21.851 --> 00:00:25.521
The three closest nation-states 
have all teamed up

00:00:25.521 --> 00:00:28.399
in what they call 
an alliance of the hungry

00:00:28.399 --> 00:00:31.611
to smash open your walls
and devour the herd.